title: Real Madrid Lifts Another Trophy
description:
The FC Crew talk Real Madrid's 2-0 victory over Eintracht Frankfurt to win the UEFA Super Cup and how their performance bodes for the upcoming season. Plus, reports surface that a hand-full of Barcelona players could leave the club if they aren't registered and the crew lookahead to Sunday's Premier League matchup between Tottenham and Chelsea.
